        <updateDate>2016-03-30T13:59:09Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Adoption Leave for Military Families Act</strong></p> <p>This bill revises adoptive leave requirements for dual military couples to permit one service member to take up to 21 days of leave and the other service member to take up to 14 days of leave. (Current law permits up to 21 days of leave for only one service member.)</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
